Class
Description

Represents a camp with its information, attendees, committees, and feedback.

Implementation of the ReportGenerator interface for generating reports on camp enquiries.

Implementation of the ReportFilter interface for filtering camps by attendee's name.

PerformanceReport
Generates a performance report based on camp committee data.
ReportFilter
The ReportFilter interface outlines the structure for implementing different filtering methods for camp data.
ReportGenerator
The ReportGenerator interface outlines the structure for generating reports based on camp data.

Main class handling staff-related operations for camps.

The main class handling operations for a student's menu.

User
